---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'SkinPen Microneedling | D-Essence Wellness',
  description:
    'Collagen-induction microneedling to refine texture, soften fine lines, minimize acne scars, and brighten tone—with tailored depths and minimal downtime.',
  canonical: '/services/skinpen-microneedling/',
  type: 'website',
  jsonLd: [
    {
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Service',
      name: 'SkinPen Microneedling',
      serviceType: 'Microneedling',
      areaServed: 'New Windsor, New York',
      provider: {
        '@type': 'MedicalBusiness',
        name: 'D-Essence Wellness',
        address: {
          '@type': 'PostalAddress',
          streetAddress: '871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102',
          addressLocality: 'New Windsor',
          addressRegion: 'NY',
          postalCode: '12553',
          addressCountry: 'US'
        }
      },
      url: 'https://dessencewellness.com/services/skinpen-microneedling/'
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ===== HERO (dark) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pt-28 pb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">
        <span>Services</span><span class="opacity-40">•</span><span>Advanced Skin Care</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">SkinPen Microneedling</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">
        Precise, heat-free microchannels prompt your skin’s own repair cycle—boosting collagen and elastin to
        smooth texture, soften fine lines, and refine scars with minimal downtime.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Good for</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Texture • Scars • Tone</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Skin types</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">I–VI (protocol-based)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Session time</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">~30–60 min</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Downtime</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Low</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTENT (white) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <div class="container py-12 sm:py-14">
      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            SkinPen creates controlled, vertical micro-channels without heat or harsh chemicals. These micro-injuries
            trigger a natural cascade—collagen and elastin remodeling—that improves texture, softens fine lines, and
            reduces the look of acne scars and enlarged pores.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Depth is tailored by area and goal. Most clients see a brighter, smoother surface within weeks, with
            progressive gains over a short series.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Helps improve</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              {[
                'Acne scars',
                'Fine lines',
                'Texture & pores',
                'Neck lines',
                'Tone & luminosity',
                'Photoaging'
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                    <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span>{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
              Final candidacy, depth, and cadence are set after an in-clinic assessment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefits -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {[
          {
            title: 'Natural collagen',
            text: 'Stimulates your own repair for firmer, smoother skin—no heat or ablative energy.'
          },
          {
            title: 'All-tone approach',
            text: 'Protocol-based settings support safe use across a wide range of skin tones.'
          },
          {
            title: 'Low downtime',
            text: 'Pinkness is common day 1–2; most resume normal routines quickly.'
          }
        ].map(card => (
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">{card.title}</div>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">{card.text}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- What to expect -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            We’ll review skin history, goals, and any active conditions. After cleansing and optional topical
            anesthetic, precise passes are made at a depth matched to each area.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Before your visit</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Arrive with clean skin (no heavy makeup on the treatment area).</li>
                <li>Pause strong actives (peels/strong retinoids) per guidance.</li>
                <li>Share medical history, allergies, and recent treatments.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">During treatment</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Topical numbing can be used for comfort.</li>
                <li>Device glides to create uniform micro-channels; sensation is a light vibration.</li>
                <li>Typical time: ~30–60 minutes depending on area.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 sm:col-span-2">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">After & timeline</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Day 0–2: pinkness, warmth, and tightness are common.</li>
                <li>Days 3–7: mild flaking can occur; glow often appears as skin settles.</li>
                <li>Weeks 2–6: progressive smoothing and tone refinement.</li>
                <li>Series: most plans include 3–6 sessions, 4–6 weeks apart.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Aftercare -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Aftercare</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Use gentle cleanser and soothing, fragrance-free moisturizer.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Daily broad-spectrum SPF; limit intense sun exposure.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Wait ~24 hours before light makeup (if skin allows).
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Avoid strong acids/retinoids, steam rooms, and vigorous workouts for 24–48 hours.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Do not pick or scrub; allow any flaking to resolve naturally.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Follow your personalized product plan between sessions.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Safety & considerations</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Common, temporary effects</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Redness, warmth, mild swelling</li>
              <li>Tightness or light flaking</li>
              <li>Small pinpoint marks that settle quickly</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Less common risks</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Irritation or post-inflammatory pigment shift (usually temporary)</li>
              <li>Infection if aftercare is not followed</li>
              <li>Uncommon scarring with inappropriate depth or technique</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Educational information only; not medical advice. Your clinician will set depths conservatively per area and tone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How many sessions will I need?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Most plans include 3–6 sessions, spaced 4–6 weeks apart, depending on concerns and response.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">When will I see results?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Early smoothness and glow often appear within 1–4 weeks; collagen remodeling continues over several weeks.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Is it painful?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Most describe a light vibration or pressure. Topical numbing helps keep sessions very tolerable.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Can it be combined with other treatments?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Yes—light peels, PRP/PRF, or curated skincare can complement results. We’ll coordinate timing to avoid excess irritation.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
            Ready to plan your microneedling series for smoother, brighter skin?
          </div>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-neutral-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-neutral-300">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
